description:
Have we fallen into deception about Eastern mysticism without knowing it? Eric Wilson was a student and instructor in martial arts for almost 25 years. During that time, he learned a great deal about the hidden dangers of these practices. In The Dragon’s Realm, he reveals the dangers of Eastern mysticism in karate, martial arts, tai chi, yoga, acupuncture, and acupressure. Learn how Eastern mysticism is an integral part of martial arts. Find out how Satan uses martial arts to control the bodies and the souls of men. 

Watch more: https://adtv.watch/
